Volkswagen South African Unit’s Sales Advanced 46%, Business Day Reports

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-05-17T05:15:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-17/volkswagen-south-african-unit-s-sales-advanced-46-business-day-reports.html
Volkswagen AG (VOW) ’s South African unit’s
sales climbed 46 percent in the first quarter compared with a
year earlier, Business Day reported, citing Volkswagen South
Africa spokesman Matt Gennrich.  Sales of the Volkswagen brand increased 31 percent from a
year earlier while Audi sales advanced 82 percent, the
Johannesburg-based newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  